{"tid":2257774,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【OVA前篇已出】刀使ノ巫女討論區(4)","createTime":"2020-10-25T13:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T10:00:03.000Z","uid":78568,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"161196a57c3d944492e7b8b8aa1674e363530c00","tid":2257774,"uid":78568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNXSaBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNXSaBA.jpg&h=a6b174ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事敘述在這個世界上，有一群被稱為「刀使」的少女，為了驅除威脅人世的怪物「荒魂」而持續戰鬥。這些少女們聚集在五所設有國中、高中部的完全中學內。這年春天，來自五所學校的刀使們齊聚一堂，面對即將展開的競技大會。身為朋友的兩位刀使立下了再戰的約定。這一約定，即使手持的御刀所向不同，也一定能化作連結之力&mdash;&mdash;可奈美的故事與美炎的故事，於此交錯。<br />\n<br />\nOVA 動畫《馭刀巫女 刻印一閃的燈火》前篇・後篇預定將在 2020 年先行播送・配信。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n監督：神谷智大<br />\n系列構成：朱白あおい（ミームミーム）<br />\n角色原案：しずまよしのり<br />\n角色設計：新妻大輔<br />\n動畫制作：project No.9<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n安桜美炎：茜屋日海夏<br />\n瀬戸内智恵：石原夏織<br />\n七之里呼吹：五十嵐裕美<br />\n六角清香：藤田茜<br />\n木寅ミルヤ：沼倉愛美<br />\n山城由依：上坂すみれ"},{"pid":"700ed1f8753540b7d1179e4cc5df659af78b0c3a","tid":2257774,"uid":78568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"OVA喺game內有幾日可以睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044d116411b61fd1ae5fd87c02e631620874218f","tid":2257774,"uid":207957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"如果唔係個死人畫風轉咗我都會俾8分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d276280aff4b026cc7b264a10656b92218aeb8","tid":2257774,"uid":207957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"有人up咗上youtube唔洗係驚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7c2f96e87438b0f6df52172d6b079d9f05f595","tid":2257774,"uid":78568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score